Sources for this project can be found at https://github.com/robitalec/comprehensive-exam and an accompanying website is at: https://robitalec.gitlab.io/comprehensive-exam/

First level package dependencies included:

- targets
- tarchetypes
- data.table
- ggplot2
- quarto
- gt
- stringr
- renv
- conflicted
- usethis
- DiagrammeR
- xfun
- magick
- googledrive
- googlesheets4

The graph visualizations were built using GraphViz [@Gansner_2000].
